{"title_page": "Dale DaBone", "text_new": "{{pp-pc1}}\n{{BLP sources|date=July 2013}}\n{{Infobox adult biography\n| name            = Dale DaBone\n| image           = Dale DaBone 2010.jpg\n| caption         = DaBone at the 2011 [[XRCO Award]]s in [[Hollywood, California]]\n| birth_name      = \n| birth_date      = {{birth date and age|1972|1|8}}\n| birth_place     = [[Greensboro]], [[North Carolina]], [[United States]]\n| death_date      =\n| death_place     =\n| spouse          =\n| nationality     = \n| height          = {{height|ft=6|in=0}}\n| weight          = {{convert|200|lb|kg st|abbr=on}}\n| alias           =                \n| number_of_films = 571 as performer & 13 as director (per [[IAFD]])\n| website         =\n}}\n\n'''Dale DaBone''' (born January 8, 1972) is an American [[pornographic actor]] and [[Film director|director]]. He has appeared in more than 500 adult movies.\n\nDaBone started in the adult film industry in 1998. DaBone had stepped away from the industry in 2003 and returned to the [[adult industry]] in 2009.<ref name=\"XBIZ\"/>\n\n==Personal life==\nDaBone was born and raised in [[Greensboro, North Carolina]].<ref name=XBIZ>{{cite web|last=Miller|first=Dan|date=July 15, 2011|title='Iron Man' Dale DaBone Discusses Mother's Tragedy|url=https://www.xbiz.com/news/136304/iron-man-dale-dabone-discusses-mothers-tragedy|publisher=[[XBIZ]]|accessdate=January 26, 2019}}</ref> He dated professional tennis player [[Jennifer Capriati]] from 2003\u20132009.<ref name=Complex>{{cite magazine|url=https://www.complex.com/sports/2014/11/athletes-dating-adult-film-stars/|title=Ballin'! A History of Athletes (Allegedly) Dating Adult Film Stars|last=Martinez|first=Jose|last2=Yuscavage|first2=Chris|last3=Evans|first3=Gavin|date=November 4, 2014|magazine=[[Complex (magazine)|Complex]]|accessdate=January 26, 2019}}</ref><ref name=BleacherReport>{{cite web|last=Sports|first=Takeo|date=October 29, 2011|title=BiBi Jones Sleeping with the Stars: Porn Stars Who Dated Fam